				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "A player hurt a party follower (i.e, not an origin nor a generic avatar). Not recorded. Preferably provide multiple alternatives. Triggers on about 1 in 5 attacks.\nThe second speaker shouldn't say anything (they're under player control). They're just included in case you want to perform tag checks on them. See also GLO_Companions_PAD_Warning_Assault"
				}
